h3. Issue Summary

If we are editing an issue and selecting an image in the description field, we will see the media toolbar, and if from that moment we click on the "Create issue"  button, the toolbar will overlay the Create screen as we see on the image below.
h3. Steps to Reproduce
 # Edit a Jira issue that has an image in the Description field;
 # Select the image so we can see the media toolbar;
 # Once you see the media toolbar, click Create issue;
 # The media toolbar is overlaid on the Create issue screen.

!Screenshot 2024-04-17 at 1.06.17 PM.png!
h3. Expected Results

The Create issue screen will be in front of all objects;
h3. Actual Results

The Create issue screen is actually been overlaid by the ;
h3. Workaround

There isn't a known workaround for it.
